text: "Hillbilly Bone" is a 2009 song by country singers Blake Shelton and Trace Adkins. It was taken from his 2009 EP Hillbilly Bone. It went to number 40 in the United States and number 84 in Canada. It made number 1 on the country charts. == References == Category:2009 songs Category:Country songs Category:Blake Shelton songs Category:Trace Adkins songs
